OL,4,CAfghan policewomen abuse: US and EU
OL,5,Curge inquiry
OL,6, The US and EU are calling for an
OL,7, immediate investigation into the
OL,8, "shocking" claims of sexual harassment
OL,9, and rape of Afghan policewomen.
OL,11,FIt follows a BBC investigation which
OL,12,Frevealed female officers faced
OL,13,Fwidespread abuse by their colleagues.
OL,15,FA number of women told the BBC they
OL,16,Fwere too scared to report the attacks,
OL,17,Fwhich were often by their superiors.
OL,19,FThe Afghan government says it is
OL,20,Fcommitted to change, but rights groups
OL,21,Fsay perpetrators are rarely punished.
